FBIS4-1541 "drchi062_k_94010" FBIS-CHI-94-062 Daily Report 3 Mar 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Handbook on Anticorruption Policy Published Handbook on Anticorruption Policy Published OW3103051094 Beijing Central Television Program One Network in Mandarin 1400 GMT 3 Mar 94 OW3103051094 Beijing Central Television Program One Network in Mandarin 1400 GMT 3 Mar 94 Mandarin BFN [From the "News" program] [Text] To support efforts to carry out the anticorruption struggle in depth, the China (Fang Zheng) Publishing House has published the Handbook on Anticorruption Policy, Laws, and Regulations. The book was compiled by the Office of Law and Regulations of the Central Discipline Inspection Commission; relevant anticorruption policies, laws, and regulations in six categories are included in the book. Cao Qingze, deputy secretary of the Central Discipline Inspection Commission and minister of supervision, wrote the book's foreword.
